---
import astroLogo from '../assets/astro.svg';
---

<div class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 py-16">
	<header class="space-y-4 text-center">
		<a href="https://astro.build" class="inline-flex justify-center">
			<img src={astroLogo.src} width="115" height="48" alt="Astro Homepage" />
		</a>
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-4xl">
			To get started, open the
			<code class="rounded-lg bg-slate-900/5 px-2 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">src/pages</code>
			directory in your project.
		</h1>
		<p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-base text-slate-600">
			Tailwind defaults handle most of the layout now, keeping the utilities light while still feeling polished.
		</p>
		<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
			<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md" href="https://docs.astro.build">
				Read our docs
			</a>
			<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-transparent px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:text-slate-900" href="https://astro.build/chat">
				Join our Discord
				<svg class="h-4 w-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 127.14 96.36">
					<path
						fill="currentColor"
						d="M107.7 8.07A105.15 105.15 0 0 0 81.47 0a72.06 72.06 0 0 0-3.36 6.83 97.68 97.68 0 0 0-29.11 0A72.37 72.37 0 0 0 45.64 0a105.89 105.89 0 0 0-26.25 8.09C2.79 32.65-1.71 56.6.54 80.21a105.73 105.73 0 0 0 32.17 16.15 77.7 77.7 0 0 0 6.89-11.11 68.42 68.42 0 0 1-10.85-5.18c.91-.66 1.8-1.34 2.66-2a75.57 75.57 0 0 0 64.32 0c.87.71 1.76 1.39 2.66 2a68.68 68.68 0 0 1-10.87 5.19 77 77 0 0 0 6.89 11.1 105.25 105.25 0 0 0 32.19-16.14c2.64-27.38-4.51-51.11-18.9-72.15ZM42.45 65.69C36.18 65.69 31 60 31 53s5-12.74 11.43-12.74S54 46 53.89 53s-5.05 12.69-11.44 12.69Zm42.24 0C78.41 65.69 73.25 60 73.25 53s5-12.74 11.44-12.74S96.23 46 96.12 53s-5.04 12.69-11.43 12.69Z"
					></path>
				</svg>
			</a>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="max-w-md space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Qwik test button</h2>
		<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Click below to make sure the Qwik integration is live.</p>
	</section>

	<a href="https://astro.build/blog/astro-5/" class="flex max-w-xl items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-slate-900 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md">
		<svg class="h-8 w-8 text-slate-900" width="32" height="32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="currentColor">
			<path
				d="M24.667 12c1.333 1.414 2 3.192 2 5.334 0 4.62-4.934 5.7-7.334 12C18.444 28.567 18 27.456 18 26c0-4.642 6.667-7.053 6.667-14Zm-5.334-5.333c1.6 1.65 2.4 3.43 2.4 5.333 0 6.602-8.06 7.59-6.4 17.334C13.111 27.787 12 25.564 12 22.666c0-4.434 7.333-8 7.333-16Zm-6-5.333C15.111 3.555 16 5.556 16 7.333c0 8.333-11.333 10.962-5.333 22-3.488-.774-6-4-6-8 0-8.667 8.666-10 8.666-20Z"
			></path>
		</svg>
		<div class="space-y-1">
			<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">What's New in Astro 5.0?</h2>
			<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
				From content layers to server islands, click to learn more about the new features and improvements in Astro 5.0
			</p>
		</div>
	</a>
</div>
